						               													<description>A solo dice game about getting back home.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Inspired on the cult film The Warriors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Postcard released in the August 2016 Board Game of the Month Club $5+ package.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;SETUP&amp;#10;A postcard game where your gang is represented by the Hearts suit (Ace to Jack), and then you will deal 6 cards to form the leaders of the other gangs, and add some more cards according to the suit.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;HOW TO PLAY&amp;#10;Roll both dice and lock a die, if possible, on one of 3 actions: Fight, Weapon, and Take Trains. Then roll the other die to get a number equal or higher to take that action, or get one of your gang cards wounded.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will be advancing in a track, having to defeat all gang members at a location before moving, or taking a train to advance anyway.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will also be able to build weapons to heal your gang or clear other enemy gang.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you make it HOME before discarding your whole gang, you win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
